high_descs: Turn right and then right into the kitchen to the countertop with the microwave on it.
Pick up the shiny pot on the counter.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the pot in the refrigerator and take the pot out.
Turn left and go to the dining table and stand between the dining table and the couch.
Put the pot on the dining table upper left-hand corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the counter top
Pick up pot from the counter top
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge
Place pot inside the fridge and then take it out
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near dining table
Place pot on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Place pot inside fridge and placing it in dining table

high_descs: Take the pot in the counter top
The pot moves towards the fridge
Open the fridge put it to the pot and take it again
Place the pot on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Pick the pot from the counter top put the pot in fridge place the pot on the dining table
